data.description: This magnificent 2020 custom home, situated on a sprawling 1 acre lot within Pasqualetti Mountain Ranch is a testament to luxury living. Boasting panoramic mountain and sunset views this meticulously crafted home offers 6 bedrooms, 4 bathrooms, designer finishes, a stunning gourmet kitchen which opens to a great room with 11' ceilings with real wood beams.  The attached casita with separate bedroom and living with a full kitchen and private entry creates a perfect 'next-gen' space or short-term rental. The owner's suite & bath create a serene experience featuring a soaking tub and walk-in shower with floor to ceiling tile. The additional 4 bedrooms and bonus/media room are oversized creating ample space for a growing family. At the heart of the expansive backyard is a stunning heated pool & spa surrounded by synthetic grass and a marvelous playground. Imagine the possibilities for expansion on this generous plot with room for an RV garage, sport court, putting green and outdoor kitchen.  This spectacular home is a canvas for you to paint a lifestyle which blends luxury, relaxation, entertainment, and a passion for family living. Check out the Amelia Spec Sheet in the documents tab to see the full list of custom home features.
